WEBVTT

04:27.392 --> 04:29.435
Hello!

04:35.650 --> 04:37.485
- Hi, Anh.
- Hello!

30:28.201 --> 30:29.035
Hello?

30:32.747 --> 30:34.332
Long time no see, bin.

30:42.924 --> 30:43.925
Hi.

30:56.396 --> 30:57.814
Yeah. That's good.

31:06.155 --> 31:08.533
No, I didn't lie to you.

31:47.780 --> 31:49.616
What do you want me to help you?

32:16.225 --> 32:22.440
In Vietnamese culture,
the kid talk to a parent like this…

32:42.418 --> 32:44.963
If I told you
that I'm married to her,

32:45.046 --> 32:48.549
you'd be angry with me that time.

32:52.553 --> 32:55.014
That's why I had to keep secret.

32:55.098 --> 32:57.141
She takes care of me good.

32:57.225 --> 32:58.559
And she a good woman.

32:59.811 --> 33:01.437
Try to understand this.

33:02.355 --> 33:04.691
I was so very lonely,

33:05.775 --> 33:08.277
and I can't live there anymore.

33:11.656 --> 33:16.077
I don't want to see anything from your mom

33:16.160 --> 33:19.914
because it would make me feel, like…

33:30.550 --> 33:33.094
I'm really sorry we don't talk.

33:33.803 --> 33:35.430
I made a mistake.

33:50.778 --> 33:53.781
I apologize for that.

33:57.744 --> 34:01.914
I want to bring her to everybody,

34:01.998 --> 34:05.168
meet everybody in our family.

34:09.839 --> 34:10.965
I love you, bin.
